companyName: iShares MSCI Emerging Markets Asia Index Fund
description:
The investment seeks to track the investment results of the MSCI Emerging Markets (EM) Asia Index.
 The fund generally will invest at least 90% of its assets in the component securities of the underlying index and in investments that have economic characteristics that are substantially identical to the component securities of the underlying index. The underlying index is designed to measure equity market performance in the emerging market countries of Asia. It may include large-, mid- or small-capitalization companies.
